&lt;h2 id=&#34;description&#34;&gt;Description:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Social media generates new types of data for quantifying human behavior, but also raises interesting research questions about the interaction between technology and society. In this course, we will learn the basics of computational social science and apply its methods in hands-on exercises to real-world data science problems.&lt;/p&gt;
